Package lexa.core.expression.map Description

This provides expression based data sets for the Lexa Expression engine.

An expression map is defined as a series of expressions in a data set. When a map data set is created, it has input data, but also the contents of the expression map.

ExpressionMap
Defines the expressions for creating the data sets.
MapDataSet
A data set based on an expression map.
